title: By the Quene. Where of late order hath ben geuen by the Quenes Maiesties commaundement, to sundry portes of this realme ... it is understand that some French vessels beyng prepared to the warre, and commyng into certayne of the sayd portes, haue ben vppon some suspicion stayed ...
author: England and Wales. Sovereign (1558-1603 : Elizabeth I)
publisher: By Richarde Iugge, and Iohn Cawood, Printers to the Queenes Maiestie,
